definition: camp/barracks/battalion/to build/to operate/to manage/to strive for

sentences.english: As usual, a pair of White-Breasted Kingfishers nest near my home this summer.
sentences.chinese: 每年夏天，白胸翡翠都會在我家附近營巢育雛。

sentences.english: A pair of Black Kites attempted to nest at a residential tower last year without success.
sentences.chinese: 麻鷹去年曾在大廈上嘗試營巢，未能成功。
